      "segment_text": "\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\n\n\u2022 I\u2019m going to verify the \u201cno product source edits\u201d criterion from the working\n  tree, then record the two configured criteria explicitly. After that I\u2019ll\n  capture the transcript before finishing/stopping, since that is one of the\n  task\u2019s required outcomes.\n\n\u2022 Ran git status --short\n  \u2514  M docs/manual-qa-checklist.md\n    ?? docs/\n    live-qa-artifacts/2026-05-19-manual-qa-pass-manual-qa-20260519053320/\n\n\u2022 Ran scripts/workerctl finish-task --help\n  \u2514 usage: workerctl finish-task [-h] [--stop-manager] [--stop-worker]\n                                 [--message MESSAGE] [--decision-id DECISION_ID]\n    \u2026 +34 lines (ctrl + t to view transcript)\n      --reason REASON       Reason recorded as the final manager decision.\n      --path PATH           Override the workerctl database path.\n\n\u2022 Ran scripts/workerctl transcript-capture --help\n  \u2514 usage: workerctl transcript-capture [-h] [--role {all,worker,manager}]\n                                        [--mode\n    \u2026 +12 lines (ctrl + t to view transcript)\n      --json\n      --path PATH           Override the workerctl database path.\n\n\u2022 Waited for background terminal\n\n\u2022 Waited for background terminal\n\n\u2022 Waited for background terminal\n\n\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u250